text: Root-seeking, destructive then regenerative. | मूल खोजी, विनाशकारी तर पुनर्जागरण। Remedies: Om Mula Namah

title: Purva Ashadha
text: Victorious, pioneering, dynamic. | विजयी, अग्रगामी, गतिशील। Remedies: Om Purvaashadha Namah

title: Uttara Ashadha
text: Steady, enduring, righteous. | स्थिर, दिर्घकालीन, धर्मपरायण। Remedies: Om Uttaraashadha Namah

title: Shravana
text: Learning, listening, scholarship. | शिक्षा, सुनाइ, विद्वता। Remedies: Om Shravanaya Namah

title: Dhanishta
text: Rhythmic, prosperous, team-oriented. | तालबद्ध, समृद्ध, टोली-उन्मुख। Remedies: Om Dhanishtha Namah

title: Shatabhisha
text: Healing, research, secrecy. | उपचार, अनुसन्धान, गोप्यता। Remedies: Om Shatabhisha Namah

title: Purva Bhadrapada
text: Mystical, transformative, visionary. | रहस्यमय, रूपान्तरणशील, दूरदर्शी। Remedies: Om Purvabhadrapada Namah

title: Uttara Bhadrapada
text: Deep, stable, wise. | गहिरो, स्थिर, बुद्धिमान। Remedies: Om Uttarabhadrapada Namah

title: Revati
text: Gentle, guiding, nourishing. | नम्र, मार्गदर्शक, पोषक। Remedies: Om Revati Namah
